graph TB
    subgraph MLflow["MLflow Tracking Server"]
        direction TB
        FastAPI["FastAPI ASGI App"]
        Flask["Flask WSGI App<br/>(legacy handlers)"]
        WSGIMiddleware["_EfficientWSGIMiddleware"]
        GraphQL["GraphQL Endpoint<br/>/graphql"]
        OTLPRouter["OTLP Trace Router<br/>/v1/traces"]
        GatewayRouter["AI Gateway Router<br/>/gateway/*/invocations"]
        AuthMiddleware["Auth Middleware<br/>(workspace-scoped RBAC)"]
        PrometheusExporter["Prometheus Exporter<br/>/metrics"]
        HueyQueue["Huey Task Queue<br/>(async jobs)"]

        FastAPI -->|wraps| WSGIMiddleware
        WSGIMiddleware -->|delegates legacy routes| Flask
        FastAPI --> GraphQL
        FastAPI --> OTLPRouter
        FastAPI --> GatewayRouter
        FastAPI --> AuthMiddleware
        FastAPI --> PrometheusExporter
        FastAPI --> HueyQueue
    end

    subgraph UI["MLflow React UI"]
        ReactApp["React SPA<br/>(experiment viz, model registry)"]
        ModuleFederation["Module Federation<br/>(compare runs, trace views)"]
        ReactApp --> ModuleFederation
    end

    subgraph Plugins["mlflow-kubernetes-plugins"]
        K8sWorkspaceStore["Kubernetes Workspace Store<br/>(kubernetes:// URI)"]
        K8sAuth["Kubernetes Auth<br/>(--app-name kubernetes-auth)"]
    end

    subgraph Clients["Client Libraries"]
        Skinny["mlflow-skinny<br/>(lightweight client)"]
        Tracing["mlflow-tracing<br/>(OpenTelemetry)"]
        CLI["MLflow CLI<br/>(Click)"]
    end

    %% User interactions
    DataScientist[Data Scientist] -->|Python SDK| Skinny
    DataScientist -->|browser| ReactApp
    DataScientist -->|CLI| CLI

    Skinny -->|REST API| AuthMiddleware
    Tracing -->|OTLP HTTP| OTLPRouter
    CLI -->|REST API| AuthMiddleware
    ReactApp -->|AJAX/GraphQL| FastAPI

    %% RHOAI Platform integration
    KubeRBACProxy["kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP → 5000/TCP"] -->|authenticated requests| FastAPI
    PlatformGateway["Platform Gateway<br/>(HTTPRoute)"] -->|443/TCP HTTPS| KubeRBACProxy

    %% Plugin integration
    AuthMiddleware -->|workspace lookup| K8sWorkspaceStore
    AuthMiddleware -->|auth check| K8sAuth

    %% External integrations
    FastAPI -->|5432/TCP| PostgreSQL["PostgreSQL<br/>(backend store)"]
    FastAPI -->|9000/TCP HTTPS| S3["S3/MinIO<br/>(artifact storage)"]
    GatewayRouter -->|443/TCP HTTPS| LLMProviders["LLM Providers<br/>(OpenAI, Anthropic, etc.)"]
    K8sWorkspaceStore -->|6443/TCP HTTPS| K8sAPI["Kubernetes API"]

    %% Module federation consumer
    EvalHub["EvalHub Dashboard"] -->|module federation| ModuleFederation

